<section class="tandem-hero-right">
  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="hero-content-right">
      <span class="section-tag">Experiencia Tándem</span>
      <h2 class="hero-description-title">
        Vive la caída libre<br />
        <span class="text-blue">sin experiencia previa</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="hero-description">
        El salto tándem está diseñado para personas que NO son paracaidistas y deseen hacer caída libre como una experiencia de vida y aventura. Es el método más popular entre aquellos que lo hacen por primera vez, haciendo que este deporte extremo sea accesible para millones de personas alrededor del mundo.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">9,000</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Pies de altura</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">140</span>
          <span class="stat-label">MPH caída libre</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">60s</span>
          <span class="stat-label">De caída libre</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://skipperu.odoo.com/shop/tdms-salto-tandem-safiro-3" class="btn-primary-large" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Ver Opciones de Salto
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#incluye" class="btn-secondary-large">
          Qué Incluye
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .tandem-hero-right {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .hero-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 80px 60px;
  }

  .hero-content-right {
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 40px;
  }

  .section-tag::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    width: 28px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--primary-blue);
  }

  .hero-description-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-text);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding: 24px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 36px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--gray-medium);
  }

  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background-color: var(--gray-light);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .btn-primary-large {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 18px 36px;
    background-color: var(--primary-blue);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-header);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: var(--transition);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-primary-large:hover {
    background-color: var(--primary-dark);
  }

  .btn-primary-large:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .btn-primary-large svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-secondary-large {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 18px 36px;
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-family: var(--font-header);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border: 2px solid var(--text-dark);
    transition: var(--transition);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-secondary-large:hover {
    background-color: var(--text-dark);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-right {
      padding: 60px 40px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-right {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .stat-divider {
      width: 48px;
      height: 1px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn-primary-large,
    .btn-secondary-large {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
